article.headline: Morgan State 64, Delaware State 60 (OT)
article.story: BALTIMORE (AP) -- Sam Brand had 15 points and seven rebounds to lead Morgan State to a 64-60 overtime victory over Delaware State on Monday night. Morgan State (9-12, 8-6 Mid-Eastern Athletic Conference) went 10-of-14 from the free throw line in overtime. Aaron Andrews had 12 points and nine rebounds for Morgan State, while Chris Grant had 12 points. Terrance Hunter led Delaware State (8-13, 7-6) with 15 points and seven rebounds, while Carlos Hawkins and Aaron Matthews each added 10 points.
